<section id="postCountSlips">
  <title>
<indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>count slips</primary>
      <secondary>posting by site</secondary>
    </indexterm>
<indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>sites</primary>
      <secondary>posting count slips in</secondary>
    </indexterm>
<indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>physical inventory</primary>
      <secondary>posting count slips</secondary>
    </indexterm>Post Count Slips</title>
  <para>To post count slip totals to their respective count
  tag totals by site, select the <guimenuitem>Post Count Slips</guimenuitem> option. The following
  screen will appear:</para>
  <para>
<screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/postCountSlips.png"/>
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Post Count Slips by Site</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot>
</para>
  <para>When posting Count Slips by site, you are
  presented with the following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry role="standard">
      <term>All Sites</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Select to post Count Slips for all sites.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry role="standard">
      <term>Selected</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Specify site where Count Slips are to be posted.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
